      "role": "user",
      "content": "joy in the little things... i dont know. it feels like trying to build a house on quicksand. if there’s no foundation, no reason why we’re even here, then the \"little things\" are just distractions. they don't change the fact that eventually everything just goes dark and stays dark. it honestly feels more real to just accept the void than to keep fighting it.",
